| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1562 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f43122f-4d5b-5cd3-8c94-3ae811f8bc14"
